    "# Hilbert-Huang Transform (HHT) 解析チュートリアル\n",
    "\n",
    "[![Open In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)](https://colab.research.google.com/github/tatsuki-washimi/gwexpy/blob/main/docs/web/en/user_guide/tutorials/advanced_hht.ipynb)\n",
    "\n",
    "このチュートリアルでは **gwexpy** の `TimeSeries.hht()` を用いた **推奨ワークフロー** を紹介します。\n",
    "HHT は非線形・非定常な信号に強く、STFT やウェーブレットでは捉えにくい瞬時周波数の変化を可視化できます。\n",
    "\n",
    "HHT は次の2ステップで構成されます:\n",
    "1. **Empirical Mode Decomposition (EMD/EEMD)**: 信号を IMF と残差に分解\n",
    "2. **Hilbert Spectral Analysis**: 各 IMF の瞬時振幅・瞬時周波数を算出\n",
    "\n",
    "**注意**: 本チュートリアルには `PyEMD` (EMD-signal) が必要です。\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "pip install EMD-signal\n",
    "```\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "ae2fea2d",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-02-26T12:41:21.100762Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-02-26T12:41:21.100237Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-02-26T12:41:23.478604Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2026-02-26T12:41:23.477650Z"
    }
   },

     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "from gwexpy.timeseries import TimeSeries\n",
    "\n",
    "# Check PyEMD availability\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    import PyEMD\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(f\"{PyEMD.__name__} is installed and ready.\")\n",
    "except ImportError:\n",
    "    raise ImportError(\n",
    "        \"This tutorial requires 'PyEMD' (EMD-signal). Please run: pip install EMD-signal\"\n",
    "    )\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "9cc7cea7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. シミュレーションデータの作成\n",
    "\n",
    "以下の非定常信号を合成します:\n",
    "- 低周波サイン (5 Hz)\n",
    "- チャープ (80 → 120 Hz)\n",
    "- 線形トレンド\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "c99ca305",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-02-26T12:41:23.481283Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-02-26T12:41:23.480746Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-02-26T12:41:45.083966Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2026-02-26T12:41:45.082742Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Plot size 1200x600 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# time / durationAxis (1seconds 、1000Sample)\n",
    "t = np.linspace(0, 1, 1000)\n",
    "dt = t[1] - t[0]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Signal minutes\n",
    "s1 = 0.5 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * 5 * t) #\n",
    "s2 = 1.0 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * 80 * t * (1 + 0.5 * t)) # (80Hz -> 120Hz)\n",
    "trend = 2.0 * t #\n",
    "\n",
    "# TimeSeries Create\n",
    "data = TimeSeries(s1 + s2 + trend, dt=dt, unit=\"V\", name=\"Simulation Data\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot\n",
    "plot = data.plot(title=\"Original Simulation Signal\")\n",
    "plot.show()\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "fa110940",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 推奨ワークフロー: `TimeSeries.hht()`\n",
    "\n",
    "`TimeSeries.hht()` は EMD/EEMD とヒルベルト解析を一括で実行します。\n",
    "ここでは次を指定します:\n",
    "- `emd_kwargs`: EEMD 設定（チュートリアルでは試行回数を少なめに設定）\n",
    "- `hilbert_kwargs`: パディングと平滑化で IF を安定化\n",
    "\n",
    "**Tip**: EEMD は確率的なので、再現性のため `random_state` を指定します。\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "dfc73f37",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-02-26T12:41:45.085759Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-02-26T12:41:45.085624Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-02-26T12:42:02.260955Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2026-02-26T12:42:02.260186Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Plot size 1000x1000 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1000x400 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "emd_kwargs = {\n",
    "    \"eemd_trials\": 20,\n",
    "    \"random_state\": 42,\n",
    "    \"sift_max_iter\": 200,\n",
    "    \"stopping_criterion\": 0.2,\n",
    "}\n",
    "hilbert_kwargs = {\n",
    "    \"pad\": 100,\n",
    "    \"if_smooth\": 11,\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "result = data.hht(\n",
    "    emd_method=\"eemd\",\n",
    "    emd_kwargs=emd_kwargs,\n",
    "    hilbert_kwargs=hilbert_kwargs,\n",
    "    output=\"dict\",\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "imfs = result[\"imfs\"]\n",
    "plot = imfs.plot(figsize=(10, 10), sharex=True, title=\"IMFs (EEMD)\")\n",
    "plot.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))\n",
    "for key in list(imfs.keys())[:3]:\n",
    "    if_ts = result[\"if\"][key]\n",
    "    plt.plot(if_ts.times.value, if_ts.value, label=key)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"Time [s]\")\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"Instantaneous Frequency [Hz]\")\n",
    "plt.title(\"Instantaneous Frequency (First 3 IMFs)\")\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "098013b2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 解釈（IMFs と IF）\n",
    "第1 IMF が高周波チャープを主に表し、瞬時周波数が時間とともに増加します。\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "829577f0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. ヒルベルトスペクトル (HHTSpectrogram)\n",
    "\n",
    "`output='spectrogram'` を指定すると時間-周波数マップを得られます。`HHTSpectrogram.plot()` は既定で対数スケールです。\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "d78580d1",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-02-26T12:42:02.262853Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-02-26T12:42:02.262719Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-02-26T12:42:19.327402Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2026-02-26T12:42:19.326555Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Plot size 1000x500 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "spec = data.hht(\n",
    "    output=\"spectrogram\",\n",
    "    emd_method=\"eemd\",\n",
    "    emd_kwargs=emd_kwargs,\n",
    "    hilbert_kwargs=hilbert_kwargs,\n",
    "    fmin=0,\n",
    "    fmax=200,\n",
    "    n_bins=120,\n",
    "    weight=\"ia2\",\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "plot = spec.plot(figsize=(10, 5))\n",
    "plot.show()\n"
   ]

   "source": [
    "## 4. 低レベルAPIについて（任意）\n",
    "\n",
    "詳細制御が必要な場合は以下を直接使用できます:\n",
    "- `emd()`（分解）\n",
    "- `hilbert_analysis()`（IA/IF）\n",
    "- `instantaneous_frequency()` / `envelope()`（個別 IMF）\n",
    "\n",
    "通常の解析では `hht()` が推奨です。\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "30f06c03",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### ヒント\n",
    "- 端点効果が出やすいので `hilbert_kwargs={'pad': N}` を検討し、端は無視してください。\n",
    "- より滑らかな IMF が必要なら `eemd_trials` を増やします（計算時間増）。\n",
    "- 再現性重視なら `emd_method='emd'` を使います。\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",

    "`TimeSeries.hht()` を使うと IMF の診断とヒルベルトスペクトルの両方を簡潔に取得できます。\n"
   ]
